  <brief_title>Compound Edaravone Injection for Acute Ischemic Stroke</brief_title>
  <official_title>Compound Edaravone Injection for Acute Ischemic Stroke, a Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Multi-dose, Parallel, and Controlled Phase II Trial</official_title>
