  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      1. To investigate the efficacy and safety of multi-doses Compound Edaravone Injection
           versus Edaravone Injection for acute ischemic stroke patients;

        2. To provide evidence for the design of Compound Edaravone Injection Phase III trial.
    </textblock>
